content.title: Wait Wait...Don't Tell Me! : NPR
content.metaDescription: Peter Sagal and Bill Kurtis host the weekly NPR News quiz show alongside some of the best and brightest news and entertainment personalities.

         ** **Saturday, ** October 11, 2025 **                          ****   Mark Tarone/Taimane/Mark Tarone                   
# Wait Wait...Don't Tell Me! for Oct 11, 2025
 Recorded in Honolulu, with host Peter Sagal, guest judge and scorekeeper Alzo Slade, Not My Job guest Taimane, and panelists Paula Poundstone, Joyelle Nicole Johnson, and Peter Grosz
      ****                   [Wait Wait...Don't Tell Me!](https://www.npr.org/programs/wait-wait-dont-tell-me/)  
### ['Wait Wait' for October 11, 2025: Live in Honolulu with Taimane!](https://www.npr.org/2025/10/11/g-s1-93098/wait-wait-for-october-11-2025-live-in-honolulu-with-taimane)
           
 
- [See Wait Wait... Don't Tell Me! sponsors and promo codes](https://www.nationalpublicmedia.com/podcastsponsors/)
 
        Live Events     Weekly Shows For tickets to our weekly shows at the **Studebaker Theater** in Chicago, [please click here](https://www.fineartsbuilding.com/events/wait-wait-dont-tell-me/)!
    Road Shows **Thursday, Oct 9** - Honolulu, HI; Blaisdell Concert Hall; 7:30pm HT; [Tickets and Info](https://www.ticketmaster.com/event/0A0062FDE5C9458E)
 **Friday, Oct 10** - Honolulu, HI; Blaisdell Concert Hall; 7:30pm HT; [Tickets and Info](https://www.ticketmaster.com/event/0A0062FDE5CB4590)
 **Thursday, Nov 6** - Costa Mesa, CA; Segerstrom Concert Hall; 7:30pm PT; [Tickets and Info](https://www.scfta.org/events/2025/wait-wait-don-t-tell-me!)
     Check back soon for more *Wait Wait… Don’t Tell Me!* events near you!

## Previous Shows
    
##  ['Wait Wait' for October 4, 2025: With Not My Job guest Becca Mann](https://www.npr.org/programs/wait-wait-dont-tell-me/g-s1-92003/wait-wait-for-october-4-2025-with-not-my-job-guest?showDate=2025-10-04) 
 October 4, 2025 • Recorded in Chicago, with guest host Negin Farsad, judge and scorekeeper Bill Kurtis, Not My Job guest Becca Mann, and panelists Shantira Jackson, Hari Kondabolu, and Adam Felber
  ****          ATTILA KISBENEDEK/Getty Images         
##  ['Wait Wait' for September 27, 2025: With Not My Job guest Cynthia Nixon](https://www.npr.org/programs/wait-wait-dont-tell-me/g-s1-90754/wait-wait-for-september-27-2025-with-not-my-job-guest?showDate=2025-09-27) 
 September 27, 2025 • Recorded in Chicago, with host Peter Sagal, judge and scorekeeper Bill Kurtis, Not My Job guest Cynthia Nixon, and panelists Negin Farsad, KC Shornima, and Adam Burke
  ****          Kristy Sparow/Getty Images         
##  ['Wait Wait' for September 20, 2025: Live in St. Louis with Not My Job guest Chip Caray!](https://www.npr.org/programs/wait-wait-dont-tell-me/g-s1-89638/wait-wait-for-september-20-2025-live-in-st-louis-with-not-my-job-guest-chip-caray?showDate=2025-09-20) 
 September 20, 2025 • Recorded in St. Louis, with host Peter Sagal, guest judge and scorekeeper Chioke I'Anson, Not My Job guest Chip Caray, and panelists Rachel Coster, Dulcé Sloan, and Adam Felber
  ****        
##  ['Wait Wait' for September 13, 2025: With Not My Job guest Bob Costas](https://www.npr.org/programs/wait-wait-dont-tell-me/g-s1-88547/wait-wait-for-september-13-2025-with-not-my-job-guest-bob-costas?showDate=2025-09-13) 
 September 13, 2025 • Recorded in Chicago, with host Peter Sagal, guest judge and scorekeeper Rhymefest, Not My Job guest Bob Costas, and panelists Brian Babylon, Emmy Blotnick, and Peter Grosz
  ****          Roy Rochlin/Getty Images         
##  ['Wait Wait' for September 6, 2025: With Not My Job guest Reneé Rapp](https://www.npr.org/programs/wait-wait-dont-tell-me/g-s1-87301/wait-wait-for-september-6-2025-with-not-my-job-guest-renee-rapp?showDate=2025-09-06) 
 September 6, 2025 • Recorded in Chicago, with host Peter Sagal, judge and scorekeeper Bill Kurtis, Not My Job guest Reneé Rapp, and panelists Alonzo Bodden, Shane O'Neill, and Amy Dickinson
